{"recipe_desc": "Warning: These are highly addictive cookies. Once you have one, you'll want three more. So make sure you have enough to share. This recipe has been passed down on my mother's family and was often Santa's favorite cookie when I was growing up.", "recipe_category": ["Desserts"], "recipe_image": ["/recipes/pecan-balls/pecan-balls.jpg"], "recipe_total_time": ["PT1H30M"], "recipe_published_time": ["Dec 19, 2011"], "image_urls": ["http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/pecan-balls/pecan-balls.jpg"], "recipe_ingredients": ["2 cups butter (softened)", "3 tablespoons sugar", "4 cups of all-purpose flour", "\u00bd teaspoon salt", "4 teaspoons vanilla extract", "4 cups chopped pecans", "1 to 2 cups powdered sugar"], "recipe_prep_time": ["PT15M"], "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<title>Pecan Ball Cookies Recipe - MakeBetterFood.com</title>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html;charset=utf-8\" />\n<link href=\"http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Brawler\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<link href=\"/css/style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<!--[if lte IE 7]>\n<link href=\"/css/ie7.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\"/>\n<![endif]-->\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" />\n<link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" title=\"MakeBetterFood.com - Recipes, Learn How to Cook Amazing Food\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/MakeBetterFood\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Pecan Ball Cookies Recipe\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"food\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/pecan-balls/\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/pecan-balls/pecan-balls.jpg\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"MakeBetterFood.com\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Warning: These are highly addictive cookies. Once you have one, you'll want three m