\"submit\" class=\"btn primary\" value=\"Search\"/>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"background\">\n<div class=\"fader\"></div>\n<img src=\"/recipes/pecan-balls/pecan-balls_large.jpg\" alt=\"Pecan Balls\" />\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid_12\">\n<div class=\"recipe\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Recipe\">\n<h1 itemprop=\"name\">Pecan Balls</h1>\n<div class=\"socialButtons\">\n<div class=\"fb-like\" data-send=\"false\" data-href=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/pecan-balls/\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"105\" data-show-faces=\"false\" data-action=\"like\"></div>\n<div class=\"pinterest\">\n<a href=\"http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.makebetterfood.com%2Frecipes%2Fpecan-balls%2F&media=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.makebetterfood.com/recipes/pecan-balls/pecan-balls_large.jpg&description=Pecan%20Balls\" class=\"pin-it-button\" count-layout=\"horizontal\">Pin It</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"print\"><a href=\"/pdfs/pecan-balls.pdf\" onclick=\"logPrintEvent('Pecan Balls');\"><img src=\"/img/icons/print.png\" alt=\"Print\" /></a><a href=\"/pdfs/pecan-balls.pdf\" onclick=\"logPrintEvent('Pecan Balls');\">Print or download (PDF)</a></div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"breadcrumbs\">\n<li><a href=\"/\">Home</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/\">Recipes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/desserts/\"><span itemprop=\"recipeCategory\">Desserts</span></a></li>\n<li>Pecan Balls</li>\n</ul>\n<div itemprop=\"description\" class=\"description\">Warning: These are highly addictive cookies. Once you have one, you'll want three more. So make sure you have enough to share. This recipe has been passed down on my mother's family and was often Santa's favorite cookie when I was growing up.</div>\n<div class=\"stats\">\n<ul>\n<li>Prep: <meta itemprop=\"prepTime\" value=\"PT15M\"/>15 min</li>\n<li>Cook: <meta itemprop=\"cookTime\" value=\"PT12to15M,5times\"/>12 to 15 min, 5 times</li>\n<li>Total: <meta itemprop=\"totalTime\" value=\"PT1H30M\"/>1 hour 30 min</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeYield\">Yields 5 dozen cookies</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"steps\">\n<div class=\"right\">\n<a href=\"/recipes/pecan-balls/pecan-balls_large.jpg\"><img class=\"polaroid\" src=\"/recipes/pecan-balls/pecan-balls.jpg\" alt=\"Pecan Balls\" itemprop=\"image\"/></a>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"direction\">Preheat the oven to 375&deg;F.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">2 cups butter (softened)</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">3 tablespoons sugar</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">In a large mixing bowl, cream butter and sugar together.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">4 cups of all-purpose flour</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">&frac12; teaspoon salt</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Add flour and salt. Mix well.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">4 teaspoons vanilla extract</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Add vanilla extract and mix well.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">4 cups chopped pecans</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">In a food processor, grind pecans so that they are very fine.</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Remove from food processor and add to dough. Mix well with a spoon or spatula.</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Using your hands, remove a small piece of dough and roll into a small ball. Place 12 (or so) balls onto a cookie sheet and bake for 12 to 15 minutes. The cookies will crack slightly.</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Repeat until dough is gone.</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Remove from oven and place on a piece of wax paper to cool. Caution: The cookies will be very fragile when they come out of the oven. Handle them with care and allow them to cool for at least 30 minutes.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">1 to 2 cups powdered sugar</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">When completely cooled, roll cookies in a bowl of powdered sugar until covered.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"footnote\">\n<div class=\"logo\">MakeBetterFood.com</div>\nFrom MakeBetterFood.com. <time itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2011-12-19\">Dec 19, 2011</time>. (http://makebetterfood.com/recipes/pecan-balls/). Adapted from Cathryn Conroy.\n</div>\n<!-- Microformat Ingredients -->\n<ul class=\"hidden\">\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">2 cups butter (softened)</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">3 tablespoons sugar</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">4 cups of all-purpose flour</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">&frac12; teaspoon salt</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">4 teaspoons vanilla extract</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">4 cups chopped pecans</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">1 to 2 cups powdered sugar</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Microformat Steps -->\n<ol class=\"hidden\">\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Preheat the oven to 375&deg;F.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">In a large mixing bowl, cream butter and sugar together.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Add flour and salt. Mix well.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Add vanilla extract and mix well.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">In a food processor, grind pecans so that they are very fine.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Remove from food processor and add to dough. Mix well with a spoon or spatula.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Using your hands, remove a small piece of dough and roll into a small ball. Place 12 (or so) balls onto a cookie sheet and bake for 12 to 15 minutes. The cookies will crack slightly.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Repeat until dough is gone.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Remove from oven and place on a piece of wax paper to cool. Caution: The cookies will be very fragile when they come out of the oven. Handle them with care and allow them to cool for at least 30 minutes.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">When completely cooled, roll cookies in a bowl of powdered sugar until covered.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notPrinted\">\n<div class=\"grid_12\">\n<div class=\"recipe\">\n<h4>Related Equipment or Ingredients</h4>\n<div class=\"pushTop10 clearfix polarioidSummaryRow\">\n<div class=\"polaroidSummary\">\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Cuisinart-DLC-10S-Classic-7-Cup-Processor/dp/B00004S9EM?SubscriptionId=AKIAJT76QZNN5CAIGPSQ&tag=makbetfoo-20&linkCode=xm2&camp=2025&creative=165953&creativeASIN=B00004S9EM\"><img src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/416SMU4gPKL.SL100_AA105.jpg\" alt=\"Cuisinart Food Processor\" class=\"\"/>\nCuisinart Food Processor</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notPrinted\">\n<div class=\"grid_12\">\n<div class=\"recipe\">\n<div class=\"grid_2 alpha\">\n<img src=\"/img/cookbook/cover_bestof_grid3.png\" alt=\"Best of Make Better Food\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 138px; width:100%;\" class=\"dropShadow\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid_10 omega\">\n<h4>Get New Recipes via Email + Free Cookbook</h4>\n<!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->\n<form action=\"http://makebetterfood.us5.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=23bb9cd41955f33d8db8c9e91&amp;id=f2cac69129\" method=\"post\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" name=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" class=\"validate clear pushTop10\" target=\"_blank\">\n<div class=\"response\" id=\"mce-error-response\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"response\" id=\"mce-success-response\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<input type=\"email\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"email\" name=\"EMAIL\" class=\"xlarge\" id=\"mce-EMAIL\" size=\"30\" onclick=\"clearEmail(this);\" onfocus=\"clearEmail(this);\" onblur=\"fillEmail(this);\" style=\"color: #222;\" required=\"required\" />\n<input type=\"submit\" class=\"btn primary\" name=\"subscribe\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe\" value=\"Subscribe and Get Your Free Cookbook\">\n</form>\n<!--End mc_embed_signup-->\n<p>Sign up to get free MakeBetterFood.com recipes via email and download a free copy of the <strong><u>Best of Make Better Food</u></strong> e-cookbook, featuring 25 of my favorite recipes.\nUnsubscribe anytime. 100% Spam Free Recipes and Emails.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</di